***********************************BOOK STORE***********************************

Problem set:
	Create a book store database using arrays, by keeping following information
	on every book.

	Name		: name of the book
	Author		: Author's name
	Publisher	: Name of the publisher(can be null)
	Year		: Book release year(can be null)

Operations to be supported:

	* Add a book to store
	* Delete a book from store
	* Display total number of books in the store
	* Print store information
	* Search Book store and list all results
		* Author
		* Book Name
		* Year of publication
		* By publisher
